âœ‹ Hand Gesture Recognition + Air Writing System
Real-time Hand Gesture Recognition and Air Writing System built using MediaPipe, OpenCV, and Google Colab (HTML + JavaScript integration).
This project allows users to detect hand gestures, add custom gestures dynamically, and write in the air using finger tracking.


