ğŸ§  How It Works
1ï¸âƒ£ Hand Detection
MediaPipe detects 21 hand landmarks./
Landmark coordinates are extracted frame-by-frame.
2ï¸âƒ£ Add Gesture      
Click "Add Gesture"
Current landmarks are captured
Assign a name to the gesture
Gesture stored in memory
3ï¸âƒ£ Gesture Recognition
Live landmarks compared with stored gestures
If matched, gesture name displayed
4ï¸âƒ£ Air Writing
Index finger tip tracked
Movement drawn on virtual canvas
Reset option available


